                                                    <label for="registerAccout">Register Account</label>
                                                </div>
                                                <div>
                                                    <input id="guestCheckout" type="radio" name="user">
                                                    <label for="guestCheckout">Guest Checkout</label>
                                                </div>

                                                <div>
                                                    <p>
                                                        By creating an account you will be able to shop faster, be
                                                        up
